5. Viewpoint: Rising global liquidity may push BTC to $130,000-140,000 in mid-summer;
6. Andrew Kang increased his Bitcoin position to $200 million, with a floating profit of about $6.8 million;
7. Viewpoint: Bitcoin holders were the first to see through the problems of US economic data;
8. Binance CEO: Companies are beginning to pay attention to areas other than traditional reserves, and BTC and digital assets will become the focus;
